<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to [Brand Name] - Your Partner in Financial Success</title>
    <style>
        /* Add some basic styling to make the email look better */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        table {
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        td {
            vertical-align: top;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <!-- Header Section -->
    <table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#212121">
        <tr>
            <td align="center">
                <a href="#" target="_blank">
                    <img src="./images/header_bg.jfif" alt="[Brand Name] Logo" width="150" height="50"
                        border="0" style="border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);" />
                </a>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#3498db">
        <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding: 40px; background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #3498db, #2980b9);">
                <h1 style="font-size: 36px; font-weight: bold; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);">
                    Welcome to [Brand Name]</h1>
                <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic;">We're thrilled to have you on board!</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <!-- Content Section -->
    <table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#ffffff">
        <tr>
            <td align="center"
                style="padding: 40px; border: 1px solid #dddddd; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
                <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #333333; font-weight: bold;">As a valued customer, you can expect
                    exceptional service, expert advice, and innovative financial solutions tailored to your needs.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #666666;">To get started, please find below your login credentials:
                </p>
                <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0;">
                    <li style="padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #cccccc;"><span
                            style="font-weight: bold;">Username:</span> [Username]</li>
                    <li style="padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #cccccc;"><span
                            style="font-weight: bold;">Password:</span> [Password]</li>
                </ul>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #666666;">If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't
                    hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:[Support Email]"
                        style="color: #3498db; text-decoration: none;">[Support Email]</a> or <a
                        href="tel:[Support Phone Number]" style="color: #3498db; text-decoration: none;">[Support Phone
                        Number]</a>.</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <!-- Footer Section -->
    <table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#212121">
        <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding: 20px;">
                <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #999999;">&copy; [Year] [Brand Name]. All rights reserved.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #999999;">Follow us on social media: <a href="#" target="_blank"
                        style="color: #3498db; text-decoration: none;"><i class="fa fa-facebook"
                            aria-hidden="true"></i></a> <a href="#" target="_blank"
                        style="color: #3498db; text-decoration: none;"><i class="fa fa-twitter"
                            aria-hidden="true"></i></a> <a href="#" target="_blank"
                        style="color: # 3498db; text-decoration: none;"><i class="fa fa-linkedin"
                            aria-hidden="true"></i></a></p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>

</html>